# read_pass generated decode artifacts (147MB — regenerable via graph_rebuild/decode).
# Commit the RECIPE (code + curated_facts.json), not the generated cake.
tools/read_pass/out/*
!tools/read_pass/out/curated_facts.json
# ...EXCEPT the "compiled brain": graph_manifest + guruji_ram are needed to RUN the
# engine + tests and are already tracked on `main` for deploy. Track them here too so
# a branch switch can NEVER delete the moat again (see PROJECT_LEDGER 2026-06-27
# "MOAT IS SPLIT"). The bulk 147MB of records/caches stays ignored.
!tools/read_pass/out/graph_manifest.json
!tools/read_pass/out/guruji_ram.json
undefined/
